reviewText: 6 disks. 22 pisodes. Judgment Day / The Gun / Skin Deep / Manifest Destiny / Breaking Point / Beholder /  Seeds of Destruction / Simon Says / Stasis / Down to Earth / Inner Child / Glitch / Decompression / Abaddon / The Grid / Revival / Gettisburg / Something About Harry / Zig Zag / Nest / Final Appeal 1.2 / Final Appeal 2.2.
They are very entertaining and the storyline for each episode is different and I think the graphics are reasonably good.
